{"tid":1542250,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(提外話) since when恐怖份子可以隨便衝紅燈 HKpolice is above laws","createTime":"2019-09-04T19:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T20:27:39.000Z","uid":61002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc9fbc75d5a8f9cb74e379cca8252a238156fa0","tid":1542250,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:53:09.000Z","msg":"<del><del></del></del><br />\n起碼一兩年前已經係咁，一到燈位前邊就着siren或者只着燈，衝完就熄返。<br />\n<br />\nFor at least 1 or 2 yrs lah.  Whenever the vehicles get close to crosswalks, they always press the alarm to signal for their &quot;privilege&quot; and to ignore the STOP red light. soon after they just turn it off like nth happens.<br />\n<br />\n咁當然，其實gespopo有特權都唔係第一日嘅事。早喺2008/09年啲示威場合，講緊仲係清汶仲有老點雙輝個年代，對住啲示威者佢哋同而家一樣會借啲意摸弦你揼下你咁。不過果陣時第一仲未係好普遍，同埋果時初初有呢啲嘢，社會輿論仲係夾到當權者做下門面功夫咁。"},{"pid":"bbb6693c64044befff49dc1a1555cfaad920157e","tid":1542250,"uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:58:13.000Z","msg":"犬隻不嬲50年代私刑打開黑社會 又收片 <br />\n7,80年代做番門面功夫 照發生<br />\n不過依家浮晒面咁解"},{"pid":"9233209dd448dbc9b6f59ec9344589e782bd793e","tid":1542250,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbb6693c64044befff49dc1a1555cfaad920157e","tid":1542250,"uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:58:13.000Z","msg":"犬隻不嬲50年代私刑打開黑社會 又收片 <br />\n7,80年代做番門面功夫 照發生<br />\n不過依家浮晒面咁解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:00:21.000Z","msg":"咁講果啲太久遠嘛。同埋計返而家啲四五十歲老差鬼都係2000年左右入職，睇壑唔係好關事"},{"pid":"93c3d7fd9d21e2a2d2376380c6b0b5a029a5373d","tid":1542250,"uid":101812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:26:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月8日百萬人大遊行 請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案</span></span><br />\n9月9號就係美國國會復會日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWBog3o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F